These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-1::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: train, jet-ski, snowmobile, subway
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: january, july, june, december
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: lacrosse, tennis, sailing, surfing
4 different games are played: bridge, canasta, monopoly, billiard
1. the person who's birthday is in july is the person driving the train##1
2. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left of the person playing canasta##1
3. the person who's sport is sailing is the person who's birthday is in january##1
4. the person driving the subway is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
5. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1
6. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the person who's sport is tennis##1
7. the person who's birthday is in july is the person playing bridge##1
8. the person who's sport is tennis is on the right of the person playing monopoly##1
9. the person driving the subway is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Transport         | train  | subway  | jet-ski | snowmobile |
| Birthday           | july | january | december  | june  |
| Sport   | surfing       | sailing      | lacrosse | tennis      |
| Game           | bridge          | canasta     | monopoly    | billiard     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-2::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: april, july, august, september
City: liverpool, san-francisco, boston, marseilles
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, rabbit, dog, goldfish
The people have 4 different jobs:  police-officer, writer, chef, lawyer
1. the person traveling to liverpool is on the far right##1
2. the owner of the goldfish is the police-officer##1
3. the person traveling to boston is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1
4. the chef is on the left of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
5. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1
6. the person who's birthday is in august is the owner of the dog##1
7. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the person who's birthday is in july##1
8. the chef is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1
9. the police-officer is on the right of the lawyer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3     |     4      |
| Birthday      | august     | april       | july | september        |
| City          | marseilles     | san-francisco       | boston   | liverpool   |
| Pet   | dog      | rabbit       | goldfish     | chinchilla    |
| Job         | chef | lawyer | police-officer | writer |

