.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-3::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: quad-bike, van, motorbike, skateboard
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: siglo, bluemaster, baccarat, aristoff
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, swimming, tennis, surfing
There 4 different types of food: peas, lime, grapefruit, mango
 1. the person driving the skateboard is the person eating mango##1
 2. the person driving the motorbike is on the far right##1
 3. the person who's sport is tennis is on the far right##1
 4. the person eating grapefruit is on the left of the person eating peas##1
 5. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the person who's sport is climbing##1
 6. the person who's sport is climbing is on the left of the person who's sport is swimming##1
 7. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the bluemaster-smoker##1
 8. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the siglo-smoker##1
 9. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the person eating mango##1
10. the person driving the motorbike is the aristoff-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |     3      |       4        |
| Transport      | van | quad-bike       | skateboard        | motorbike        |
| Cigar           | bluemaster   | baccarat | siglo   | aristoff |
| Sport   | climbing     | swimming    | surfing | tennis        |
| Food           | grapefruit         | peas  | mango       | lime         |

