.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-4::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: epic, musical, family, horror
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: siglo, fonseca, ritmeester, chaman
4 different games are played: domino, snooker, whist, poker
The people use 4 different means of transport: tram, scooter, van, ship
1. the person playing whist is on the left of the person watching epic movies##1
2. the person watching family movies is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
3. the siglo-smoker is on the far right##1
4. the person watching horror movies is on the left of the person driving the tram##1
5. the siglo-smoker is on the right of the fonseca-smoker##1
6. the chaman-smoker is on the right of the person watching musical movies##1
7. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the person watching epic movies##1
8. the person playing domino is on the far right##1
9. the person driving the van is the person playing poker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3     |      4      |
| Movie-Genre           | musical   | epic  | horror | family |
| Cigar   | ritmeester | chaman       | fonseca       | siglo     |
| Game   | whist       | poker    | snooker     | domino  |
| Transport           | scooter     | van | ship     | tram         |

