.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-5::.
There 4 different types of food: apricot, garlic, onion, pineapple
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: october, november, december, september
4 different pets are kept: rat, mouse, dog, guinea-pig
The people have 4 different hobbies: magic-tricks, writing, baking, collecting
1. the person who's birthday is in december is on the far left##1
2. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the person eating apricot##1
3. the person who's hobby is writing is on the far left##1
4. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the owner of the rat##1
5. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
6. the person who's hobby is collecting is the owner of the dog##1
7. the owner of the rat is on the left of the person who's birthday is in october##1
8. the person eating garlic is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
9. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the person eating onion##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |       3       |      4       |
| Food           | apricot  | onion    | garlic | pineapple |
| Birthday   | december      | november    | october         | september    |
| Pet   | mouse   | rat     | dog          | guinea-pig      |
| Hobby         | writing | magic-tricks | collecting      | baking      |

