.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-6::.
City: miami, marseilles, rome, edinburgh
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, sunflower, tulip, aconite
There are 4 different nationalities: canadian, egyptian, russian, british
House: gothic-revival, art-deco, palace, modern
 1. the person traveling to rome is the canadian##1
 2. the person traveling to miami is the egyptian##1
 3. the person who growsamaryllis is the canadian##1
 4. the palace house is the person traveling to miami##1
 5. the russian is the person who growsaconite##1
 6. the person traveling to rome is on the left of the person traveling to marseilles##1
 7. the person who growstulip is on the left of the modern house##1
 8. the canadian is on the right of the russian##1
 9. the person who growstulip is on the far left##1
10. the gothic-revival house is on the left of the person traveling to marseilles##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |     3      |     4     |
| City          | miami  | edinburgh | rome     | marseilles |
| Flower           | tulip  | aconite      | amaryllis | sunflower    |
| Nationality   | egyptian | russian  | canadian    | british  |
| House           | palace   | modern       | gothic-revival       | art-deco      |

