There 4 different types of food: raspberry, garlic, cabbage, radish
 1. the person traveling to san-francisco is the person playing monopoly##1
 2. the person eating radish is on the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
 3. the person who's sport is surfing is on the right of the person playing whist##1
 4. the person traveling to marseilles is on the left of the person playing whist##1
 5. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the person traveling to boston##1
 6. the person playing whist is on the left of the person playing billiard##1
 7. the person traveling to san-francisco is the person eating cabbage##1
 8. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the far left##1
 9. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
10. the person eating raspberry is on the left of the person eating cabbage##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Sport    | skateboarding | weightlifting     | surfing    | cycling |
