5. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the wooden house##1
6. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the ritmeester-smoker##1
7. the person who's hobby is reading is the ritmeester-smoker##1
8. the vegafina-smoker is the wooden house##1
9. the dunhill-smoker is the cape-cod house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |      3      |     4      |
| House      | art-deco      | wooden         | palace        | cape-cod      |
