4. the canadian is on the right of the videographer##1
5. the turkish is on the left of the person traveling to boston##1
6. the polish is the person traveling to nizza##1
7. the canadian is the analyst##1
8. the person playing billiard is on the far left##1
9. the person playing go is the person traveling to nizza##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |      3      |     4      |
