.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-10::.
There 4 different types of food: tomato, orange, artichoke, apple
4 different games are played: backgammon, go, billiard, whist
4 different pets are kept: mouse, bird, snake, fish
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: march, january, may, november
1. the person playing whist is on the right of the person eating orange##1
2. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1
3. the person eating tomato is on the far left##1
4. the person eating artichoke is the person playing whist##1
5. the person eating apple is on the left of the owner of the bird##1
6. the person playing go is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1
7. the owner of the fish is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1
8. the person playing go is the person eating apple##1
9. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |    3     |      4      |
| Food      | tomato     | apple           | orange    | artichoke    |
| Game         | billiard  | go | backgammon  | whist |
| Pet   | snake     | mouse     | bird | fish   |
| Birthday         | november | march     | january | may     |

