The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: thriller, romance, disaster, documentary
There 4 different types of food: spinach, pumpkin, cherry, pineapple
There are 4 different favourite colors: blood-red, fuchsia, grey, pink
 1. the person watching disaster movies is on the left of the person eating pineapple##1
 2. the person watching disaster movies is the fan of metal##1
 3. the person who likes blood-red is the fan of disco##1
 4. the fan of disco is on the right of the person eating spinach##1
 5. the fan of soul is on the far left##1
 6. the person eating pineapple is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1
 7. the person eating cherry is on the far right##1
 8. the person watching thriller movies is the person who likes grey##1
 9. the fan of classical is on the right of the person watching documentary movies##1
10. the person who likes pink is on the right of the fan of disco##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |      2       |        3        |      4      |
| Music-Genre       | soul     | metal    | disco         | classical  |
| Movie-Genre         | thriller | disaster | documentary | romance |
| Food       | pumpkin    | spinach     | pineapple          | cherry      |
| Color   | grey  | fuchsia    | blood-red      | pink       |

