.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-20::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: emerald, green, ivory, white
4 different games are played: scrabble, bridge, billiard, backgammon
House: townhouse, modern, wooden, ranch-style
There are 4 different nationalities: italian, chinese, german, american
 1. the person playing bridge is on the far right##1
 2. the person playing scrabble is on the right of the townhouse house##1
 3. the person who likes ivory is on the right of the modern house##1
 4. the person who likes emerald is the wooden house##1
 5. the person who likes white is on the left of the person who likes green##1
 6. the person who likes ivory is on the far right##1
 7. the american is on the right of the person playing billiard##1
 8. the wooden house is the chinese##1
 9. the german is on the far right##1
